N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 107.5 - Department of Taxation and Finance

State Regulations

As used in this Subchapter, the terms Department and

Department of Taxation and Finance mean the Division of Taxation of the New

York State Department of Taxation and Finance unless the text clearly requires
a different meaning. Notes
